OPAL harmonic analysis
======================

Library to analyse harmonic components of field OPAL fields and build transfer
maps based on those components.

Modules
-------

harmonic_analysis: loads a field from OPAL (via python interface) and calculate
harmonics of the field at a point or along a trajectory

transfer_map: [in development] based on the harmonic components of the field,
calculates the infinitesimal transfer map that transports a particle from s to
s+ds

tracking_analysis: [in development] based on an infinitesimal step through the
OPAL tracking, estimates the infinitesimal transfer map that transports a
particle from s to s+ds

polynomial_fit: support routines for tracking_analysis. Given a set of input
positions u_i and output positions v_j, guess what is the polynomial that
maps the u_i to v_i

meta_analysis: compare the transfer map calculated by transfer_map to the transfer
map calculated by tracking_analysis. Do they agree?

plot_dump_em_fields: [not used] plots the field from OPAL

multipolet_dipole_analysis: [in development]


